---
---

<section class="trust-section" aria-labelledby="trust-heading" data-gsap="reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="trust-header">
      <div class="trust-kicker">Trust &amp; Recognition</div>
      <h2 class="trust-title" id="trust-heading">Institutional Standing</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="trust-grid">
      <!-- Registered Society -->
      <div class="trust-card">
        <div class="trust-card-kicker">Registered Society</div>
        <h3 class="trust-card-heading">Bhopal Camera Club</h3>
        <dl class="trust-specs">
          <div class="trust-spec">
            <dt class="spec-label">Registration Act</dt>
            <dd class="spec-value">MP Society Registrikaran Adhiniyam 1973</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-spec">
            <dt class="spec-label">Registration Date</dt>
            <dd class="spec-value">October 2019</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-spec">
            <dt class="spec-label">Registration Number</dt>
            <dd class="spec-value spec-value--muted">[society.regNumber]</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-spec trust-spec--last">
            <dt class="spec-label">Registered City</dt>
            <dd class="spec-value">Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
        <p class="trust-body">The club is a registered non-profit society governed by the MP Society Registrikaran Adhiniyam 1973. Its constitution, its membership structure, and its processes are documented and legally recognised — a foundation of institutional trust for members and partners alike.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FIP -->
      <div class="trust-card">
        <div class="trust-card-kicker">National Federation</div>
        <h3 class="trust-card-heading">Federation of Indian Photography</h3>
        <dl class="trust-specs">
          <div class="trust-spec">
            <dt class="spec-label">Membership Class</dt>
            <dd class="spec-value">Corporate Member</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-spec">
            <dt class="spec-label">Member Number</dt>
            <dd class="spec-value spec-value--gold">CM1098</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-spec">
            <dt class="spec-label">Affiliation</dt>
            <dd class="spec-value">FIP · India</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-spec trust-spec--last">
            <dt class="spec-label">Future Partnerships</dt>
            <dd class="spec-value spec-value--muted">Space reserved</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
        <p class="trust-body">Bhopal Camera Club holds Corporate Membership of the Federation of Indian Photography — the national body for photography organisations in India. This affiliation opens access to national competitions, exhibitions, and a broader community of photography organisations across the country.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.trust-section {
  background: var(--surface-1);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  padding: 96px 0;
}
.trust-header {
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}
.trust-kicker {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-600);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.trust-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 40px);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  color: var(--ink-900);
}

/* Grid */
.trust-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  background: var(--surface-0);
}
.trust-card {
  padding: 48px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--hairline);
}
.trust-card:last-child {
  border-right: none;
}
.trust-card-kicker {
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-600);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
}
.trust-card-heading {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  color: var(--ink-900);
}

/* Specs list */
.trust-specs {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.trust-spec {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: baseline;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline-soft);
  padding-bottom: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  gap: 12px;
}
.trust-spec--last {
  border-bottom: none;
  margin-bottom: 0;
  padding-bottom: 0;
}
.spec-label {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--ink-400);
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.spec-value {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--ink-900);
  text-align: right;
}
.spec-value--gold {
  color: var(--gold-500);
  font-weight: 600;
}
.spec-value--muted {
  color: var(--ink-400);
}
.trust-body {
  font-size: 13px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--ink-600);
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .trust-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .trust-card {
    border-right: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    padding: 36px 28px;
  }
  .trust-card:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
}
</style>
